26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_i2c_padgf119.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:34 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "pad.h"
30#include "aux.h"
31#include "bus.h"
32
33static const struct nvkm_i2c_pad_func
34gf119_i2c_pad_s_func = {
35 .bus_new_4 = gf119_i2c_bus_new,
36 .aux_new_6 = g94_i2c_aux_new,
37 .mode = g94_i2c_pad_mode,
38};
39
40int
41gf119_i2c_pad_s_new(struct nvkm_i2c *i2c, int id, struct nvkm_i2c_pad **ppad)
42{
43 return nvkm_i2c_pad_new_(&gf119_i2c_pad_s_func, i2c, id, ppad);
44}
45
46static const struct nvkm_i2c_pad_func
47gf119_i2c_pad_x_func = {
48 .bus_new_4 = gf119_i2c_bus_new,
49 .aux_new_6 = g94_i2c_aux_new,
50};
51
52int
53gf119_i2c_pad_x_new(struct nvkm_i2c *i2c, int id, struct nvkm_i2c_pad **ppad)
54{
55 return nvkm_i2c_pad_new_(&gf119_i2c_pad_x_func, i2c, id, ppad);
56}
